      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 100,
      "message": "My suggestions would be:\n1. If only one region in openstack, openstack plugin should be able to automatically discover and use it. No need to specify.\n2. If multiple regions in openstack, a default region should be specify on VIM registering through a new key \"openstack-region-id\"\n3. Considering ESR is the blocker, using \"cloud-extra-info\" as a temporarily store of \"openstack-region-id\" could be consider as a workaround in R3 release.",
